-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;消息人士称，&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;美国官员正在研究&lt;/strong&gt;油价可能飙升至每桶 200 美元对经济意味着什么，这表明特朗普政府正在为伊朗战争的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/oX1NqXJtp8UYGGdaEX4IB5bW10Z97tOb19iHjj0J-NAPraYXTFlBVa9r0qP-ev87BdvEYkfxIhUWJB6Na49LtyzEaNOzkrPARbjWzqK3DgZHg3qCvcX2flmGyv6P7_PUF0txysxI2Rk_6kOqkJg9KPR7Ji-2aKapMu1-BcJV5_pNaNxcUIMuE_1NRgRjYSTwHxiQS9Mgt97qZm4qZ1OqbKVLRJ6b_rJoZTXMK92sI4_mwF5MroXLkTQyOU7ahqcHm6t_tMrsyTu_02HYUPPRy78JPLeaWTXgqB-nTyYXcNdpPuGyDGGD9jVM5kJ9_-jsZFDkT9GyBJLX0rnLBSYhT9jJ8hqvox03IYEuRaTgOo7D_01pq_pWDuf0ATqrfi6vi_PMaQXJrr3nLayrKBnqPys1pq-PWvlnjqhXI38M4VQNtS-eFz7yrVIPliDYZ0vnJkukeJLT8drUfuqvqZBgODq-gueC2PM-Tb582CuaU5D2XL4WwSbxg8ng0Z1qwfKxeUFmqaSWkpfnrVZ1O6nSzw/_XJK_SZr3aTeo25l777WE8aOcHeZt8Pq/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="特朗普团队研究每桶 200 美元的油价意味着什么"&gt;极端情况&lt;/a&gt;做准备。他们表示，这一努力不是预测，而是旨在确保政府为所有突发事件做好准备，包括长期冲突。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/tP0BWZTOAc0YhLR-Kd_hBnEg2K7CJGlRJEtkRcNtq-kwnX63U28xOI-lUKIuBqSV6_F1eBlLNHn1nKO7gPj8_UUMyX8Sm2v0YIOFFGQK-1upsJ5MgNi-CQD-P82MSM49NE5-H7KIJGLPgoyntmOmqjV0xgZgVJHcESDAIZFcZiIiKXnz8OtXdYbSn9pAcrQsuBvxSZRFRkEMg6JBMIJ1HlEk4Dkb2IHdNtvX2bgqksM3PGiN4jAzbzl7w_cvp7ofuEl7QYjCVZ553R-s0ZdAaJO3ThV6r45sAQzbk3MTplIoqo6Y0LsqPVN0HPrXYhv-ZM7tVxqVDUu_iQRTDkoWSGBWzvfvndMOGaNQ3fnKs4XVl1ODevvViICIrD0cJKtHGRvqVeFe5NjQBsg/W-o1HOWDz-2N9liKpkvo8fmT5YD4Tich/19" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ioNtEGrji.qM/v27/-1x-1.jpg" alt="Military strikes are continuing in the Middle East as US President Donald Trump’s Friday deadline for Iran to negotiate a deal to end the war approaches. Israel said it struck infrastructure in Isfahan, in the center of Iran, while the UAE and Bahrain reported Iranian missile and drone threats. Iran’s armed forces said they carried out missile strikes targeting American forces and separatist groups backed by the US-Israeli alliance in the northern Iraqi city of Erbil. Bloomberg&amp;amp;#39;s Joumanna Bercetche reports." width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="随着美国总统唐纳德·特朗普周五为伊朗谈判结束战争协议的最后期限临近，中东的军事打击仍在继续。以色列表示，它袭击了伊朗中部伊斯法罕的基础设施，而阿联酋和巴林则报告了伊朗的导弹和无人机威胁。伊朗武装部队表示，他们对伊拉克北部城市埃尔比勒的美军和美以联盟支持的分裂主义团体进行了导弹袭击。彭博社的 Joumanna Bercetche 报道。" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ioNtEGrji.qM/v27/-1x-1.jpg" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4;"&gt;观看：彭博社的 Joumanna Bercetche 报道了伊朗战争的最新进展。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;与此同时，&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;亚洲各国政府&lt;/strong&gt;正在为最坏的能源情景做准备，其中可能包括长期严重的供应中断。中东冲突爆发不到一个月，各国已进入&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/DU9d5zuj2wrzng7cZdyrH2AKjYghxqyh_yu3Th841FsuLKIa7slDxPxEQojdhJspuPRncWzouunn2URCcakEtJw4q6cWzlnZ8rimZEn1RlIP1h4rZ1Ht3elMdnYxzq4qLZKX2B-hRWtF3Criq7brhCtbmPHhuW6CB9jTRSqZtuE3kCMDpgXFLW5Shu5R0C1_Rzs0Pqcjf8S4VH7ohs0wafbg2PChJCgC2IV4t_APggK08_uHTsgXi-WJ8uBPDXQrVaJq301ApSp6E85yemmBn0mXF6m7wCSm3v4EXVMj7uBOFgNY_htgbjZ-J_q0NMqYZYJXGKixFneXizH5KTidaYawCLFCSLUTirZNgw0df5Vnkmo_YQdSuBltyOqnYCx6nyc45ZsVe8aRM8CHCR1NtHkIX_JgvnCGy2TqrW5S_eUxI0fe18HUVYFwPxJn4lJb2RBw_c0ROuk1s7FGhDT1-AQoA9wwpp_nBKkOrJiW7tXEp9Se_-ExqiOTpkTTNOlVRJEOHgcKZ3bpyK-mCqLRE5M/Gf3qseokMUFncO9vh2xoYQF4u8UmeGqh/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="随着伊朗战争的持续，亚洲准备迎接最坏的能源情景"&gt;紧急状态&lt;/a&gt;，工作周缩短，路灯关闭，加油站被迫关闭。国际货币基金组织正在规划，如果战争持续下去，哪些经济体可能&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/9exRDTl-yEgrh0yalY07tBENZAmfmqq5U3kNTHPw4CNqrLL5szY2tCj5n-eOFHKsqDj3Jn0OZ4Vd4bBxSkEtpUwrZuUG-Z3ZsQZ-u